text: Afesha Olton-Humphreys (born 22 May 1992) is a Trinidad and Tobago female volleyball player. She was part of the Trinidad and Tobago women's national volleyball team. She participated in the 2017 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. == References == == Other websites == * Trinidad & Tobago to debut at World Championship *Esdelle, Thompson head missing vball stars *Afesha Olton - Volleyball player profile & career statistics - Global Sports Archive Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Trinidad and Tobago volleyball players
